<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7345> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7345" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Prefect under Cicero in Cilicia in 51-50 (MRR 2.246, 254). He was very probably father of L. Volusius Saturninus, Cos. suff. 12, one of a family which, according to Tacitus (Ann. 3.30), had not risen beyond the praetorship. Hence he may have become a praetor. See Wiseman, CQ 14, 1964, 126, and NM 277- 278. no. 514; Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 156 (on his marriage to a Claudia) -RP 2.605-606.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5495> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5495" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Cicero in Cilicia (Cic. Fam. 5.20.4). See 51, Prefects." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5435> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5435" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent to Cyprus by Cicero to attend to the litigation of the Roman citizens there (Cic. Att. 5.21.6; the praenomen Cn. in Att. 5.11.4 may be an error)." .
